# EU Scout Web App — local development environment
# Copy this file to .env.local and fill in your values.
# ⚠️  NEVER commit .env.local or any file containing real API keys.

# ── Optional: Claude API key (if you want cloud AI instead of local LLM) ──────
# Stored encrypted in the browser (AES-256-GCM) — this is just for local dev
# VITE_CLAUDE_API_KEY=sk-ant-api03-...

# ── Dev proxy overrides (Vite proxies these in vite.config.ts) ────────────────
# These match the nginx proxy paths in nginx.conf — no change needed for dev.
# EU Funding & Tenders API → /api/eu/*
# OpenCorporates API       → /api/opencorporates/*
